fm: vector<int> pancakeSort(vector<int> A) {         vector<int> res;         int x,i;         for (x = A.size(); x > 0; --x) {             for (i = 0; A[i] != x; ++i);             reverse(A.begin(), A.begin() + i + 1);             res.push_back(i + 1);             reverse(A.begin(), A.begin() + x);             res.push_back(x);         }         return res;     }

fm: vector<int> powerfulIntegers(int x, int y, int bound) {         set<int> s;         vector<int> ret;         int i = 1, j = 1;         while (i + j <= bound) {             while (i + j <= bound) {                 s.insert(i + j);                 if (y == 1)                     break;                 j *= y;             }             j = 1;             if (x == 1)                 break;             i *= x;         }         for (auto m:s)             ret.push_back(m);         return ret;     }

vector<int> flipMatchVoyage(TreeNode *root, vector<int> &voyage) {         if (!root || voyage.size() == 0)             return {};         this->voyage = voyage;         nodes.clear();         index = 0;         helper(root);         if (!match)             return {-1};         return nodes;     }

fm: int subarraysDivByK(vector<int> &A, int K) {         auto size = A.size();         unordered_map<int, int> count;         int ret = 0, prefix = 0;         count[0] = 1;         for (int a : A) {             prefix = (prefix + a) % K;             if (prefix < 0) prefix += K;             ret += count[prefix];             ++count[prefix];         }         return ret;     }
